# Token Efficiency Rules

- Implement only one checklist task at a time from `todos/phase-*.md`.
- Keep output concise: changed files, commands, outcomes.
- Request patch-style edits instead of broad rewrites.
- Prefer reading specific files over wide repo scans.
- Reuse prompt templates from `IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md`.
- Stop after a shippable checkpoint and verify tests.
